Title: API: modification of time period endpoint to support built-in time period
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: core
Date: 1613385021
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0b8

This change introduces the possibility to get information
about the default built-in time period "24X7" through the
show timeperiod endpoint.
